Comments: Must have SSD1306 controller and these 6 pins: GND  VCC  SCL  SDA  RST  D/C (picture here  http://i.imgur.com/y3cWazS.jpg).  Manufacturer is http://www.heltec.cn. Heltec also similar blue models (with sh1063 controller) and 'new' models with different 6 pins (VCC and GND swapped  no RST pin)  these two models are incompatible with the current POWER PLAY design.
Order the PCB from your favorite PCB manufacturer (2 layers  60x60mm).  Make sure to order a SMD stencil  preferably 5mil stainless steal but even a 5 mil stencil from oshstencils.com should work.
